  "subject": "📊 Daily Portfolio: +10.3% | AVGO earnings tonight — hold or trim?",
  "html_body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f5f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #111827;\">\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color: #f4f5f7; padding: 24px 12px;\">\n  <tr><td align=\"center\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width:600px;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n\n    <!-- HERO -->\n    <tr><td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b 0%,#334155 100%);padding:32px 24px;color:#fff;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#94a3b8;\">Daily Portfolio Check</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:4px 0 2px;font-size:14px;color:#cbd5e1;\">Wednesday, June 3, 2026 — 11:05 PM Kuwait Time</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;\">Portfolio last updated: May 13, 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 5 positions &nbsp;|&nbsp; Cost basis: $706.99</p>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;\">Total P&amp;L (vs cost basis)</p>\n          <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#10b981;\">+$73.04 <span style=\"font-size:18px;opacity:.8;\">(+10.33%)</span></p></td>\n          <td align=\"right\" valign=\"bottom\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;\">NVDA today ✓</p>\n          <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#10b981;\">+$7.24 (+2.34%)</p></td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n      <p style=\"margin:16px 0 0;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid #475569;font-size:13px;color:#e2e8f0;\">NVDA +2.3% on Computex PC chip launch (N1X co-developed with Microsoft). AVGO Q2 FY26 earnings out TONIGHT ~5 PM ET — options market pricing ±8% move.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n\n    <!-- DECISIONS NEEDED -->\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 24px;background:#fef3c7;border-bottom:1px solid #fde68a;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#92400e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;\">⚠️ Decisions needed</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:6px 0 2px;font-size:14px;color:#78350f;\"><strong>AVGO:</strong> TP1 at $474 hit. Earnings tonight at 5 PM ET (1 AM Kuwait). Watch after-hours — make hold/trim/exit call before tomorrow's open.</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#92400e;\"><strong>TSM &amp; AMD:</strong> Both above TP1 but commission math fails at current prices. Levels: TSM &gt;$441.93, AMD &gt;$531.40.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n\n    <!-- DATA NOTE -->\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:8px 24px;background:#f8fafc;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;\">⚠️ <strong>Price note:</strong> NVDA = June 3 intraday (CNBC, ~4 PM ET). LLY / AVGO / TSM / AMD = June 2 confirmed closes — June 3 official closes not yet indexed at report time.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n\n    <!-- SNAPSHOT TABLE -->\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:24px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;\">Position Snapshot</p>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;\">\n        <thead><tr style=\"background:#f9fafb;\">\n          <th style=\"text-align:left;padding:10px 8px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Status</th>\n          <th style=\"text-align:left;padding:10px 8px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th>\n          <th style=\"text-align:right;padding:10px 8px;f