12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:600;\">TSM <span style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;\">Jun 2</span></td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$441.00</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+1.23%</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$11.79</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-weight:600;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+13.55%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">⚠️ WATCH</span></td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-weight:600;\">AMD <span style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;\">Jun 2</span></td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">$516.00</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#6b7280;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">~+3%</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$10.20</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;text-align:right;color:#059669;font-weight:600;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+20.33%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr style=\"background:#f9fafb;\">\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding:12px 8px;font-weight:700;\">TOTAL INVESTED</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;text-align:right;color:#6b7280;\">$780.03</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;text-align:right;color:#6b7280;\">—</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+$73.04</td>\n            <td style=\"padding:12px 8px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;color:#059669;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">+10.33%</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n      <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;\">Cash: $15.00 — Total portfolio incl. cash: $795.03</p>\n    </td></tr>\n\n    <!-- POSITION DETAIL CARDS -->\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0 24px 24px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;\">Position Detail</p>\n\n      <!-- NVDA -->\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n            <td><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">NVDA</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background:#d1fae5;color:#059669;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">✅ HOLD</span></td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">$229.61 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:13px;\">+2.34%</span></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5;\">Post-earnings momentum continues. Jensen Huang's Computex keynote unveiled the N1X PC chip (co-developed with Microsoft) — NVDA's first consumer CPU, expanding TAM beyond the datacenter. Approaching TP1 at $240 (4.5% away). May 20 earnings beat is priced in; the PC narrative is a fresh catalyst. No action.</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$204.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$240.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$260.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$285.00</strong></td>\n          </tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- LLY -->\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n            <td><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">LLY</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background:#d1fae5;color:#059669;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">✅ HOLD</span></td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">$1,070.57 <span style=\"color:#dc2626;font-size:13px;\">-1.07%</span></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5;\">Foundayo (orforglipron) FDA-approved April 2026 — the oral GLP-1 launch is live and the catalyst is priced in. The 1% dip on June 2 is noise. Up 7.6% from entry, TP1 at $1,114 is 4.1% away. Zero correlation to the AI semi trade — this is your portfolio's risk anchor. No binary events near-term.</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$915.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$1,114</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$1,243</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$1,393</strong></td>\n          </tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- AVGO -->\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:2px solid #ea580c;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n            <td><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">AVGO</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background:#ffedd5;color:#ea580c;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">🔔 ACTION</span> <span style=\"margin-left:4px;padding:2px 8px;background:#fecaca;color:#b91c1c;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">EARNINGS TONIGHT</span></td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">$487.00 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:13px;\">+5.88%</span></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 6px;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5;\">TP1 at $474 has been cleared — AVGO is +18.2% from entry. Q2 FY26 earnings drop tonight after close (~5 PM ET = 1 AM Kuwait). Consensus: EPS $2.40, Rev $22.12B. Q2 AI revenue guided to $10.7B (+140% YoY). Broadcom has beaten EPS every quarter for the last 4 in a row. The options market prices ±8% move.</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background:#fff7ed;border-left:3px solid #ea580c;border-radius:4px;margin:8px 0;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:10px 12px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#c2410c;\">Commission math — TP1 trim (50% = 0.1575 shares @ $487):</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:12px;color:#7c2d12;font-family:monospace;\">Gross: +$11.81 | Commission: −$6.00 | Net: +$5.81</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#c2410c;\">Full exit (0.315 shares @ $487):</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#7c2d12;font-family:monospace;\">Gross: +$23.62 | Commission: −$6.00 | Net: +$17.62</p>\n            </td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px;font-size:13px;color:#1e3a5f;line-height:1.5;font-weight:600;\">Recommendation: HOLD through earnings.</p>\n          <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;\">The TP1 trim nets only $5.81 — not worth trading out before a likely beat. If Q2 beats and Q3 guide clears $24B, target TP2 at $536 next session (net +$13.52 — far more compelling). Watch 1 AM Kuwait for AH reaction:</p>\n          <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#374151;line-height:1.8;\">• <strong>AH &gt;+5%:</strong> Prepare TP2 trim at $536 next session<br>• <strong>AH flat / ±3%:</strong> Hold, resume TP ladder<br>• <strong>AH &lt;−5%:</strong> Exit full position at tomorrow's open — lock the +$17.62 net gain, don't ride a miss to the $379 stop</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$379.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <strong style=\"color:#ea580c;\">$474 ✓ HIT</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$536.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <strong style=\"color:#6b7280;\">N/A</strong></td>\n          </tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- TSM -->\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n            <td><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">TSM</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">⚠️ WATCH</span> <span style=\"margin-left:4px;padding:2px 8px;background:#fecaca;color:#b91c1c;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">HIGH GEO RISK</span></td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">$441.00 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:13px;\">+1.23%</span></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5;\">TP1 at $435 is hit — TSM is +13.6% from entry. However, the partial trim math fails (gross $5.90 &lt; $6 threshold). TSM is also the highest-risk position in the portfolio (52/100, HIGH) due to Taiwan Strait binary tail risk. No geopolitical escalation signals today — risk is latent. NVDA's Computex PC announcement is actually a read-through bullish for TSMC demand.</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background:#fefce8;border-left:3px solid #d97706;border-radius:4px;margin:8px 0;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:10px 12px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#92400e;\">Commission math — TP1 trim (50% = 0.112 shares @ $441):</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#78350f;font-family:monospace;\">Gross: +$5.90 | Commission: −$6.00 | Net: −$0.10 → HOLD (commission eats profit)</p>\n              <p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#78350f;\">Threshold: TSM needs to close &gt;$441.93 before gross clears $6.</p>\n            </td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:10px;\"><tr>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;\">Stop: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$357.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP1: <strong style=\"color:#d97706;\">$435 ✓ HIT</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:center;\">TP2: <strong style=\"color:#111827;\">$485.00</strong></td>\n            <td style=\"font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;text-align:right;\">TP3: <strong style=\"color:#6b7280;\">N/A</strong></td>\n          </tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- AMD -->\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 16px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr>\n            <td><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:700;\">AMD</span> <span style=\"margin-left:8px;padding:2px 8px;background:#fef3c7;color:#d97706;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">⚠️ WATCH</span></td>\n            <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;\">$516.00 <span style=\"color:#059669;font-size:13px;\">~+3%</span></td>\n          </tr></table>\n          <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.5;\">TP1 at $493 hit — AMD is up 20.3% from entry, touched all-time high $527.20 on May 28. Seaport upgraded to Buy citing TSMC allocation gains for MI300X AI GPUs. Next real catalyst is Q2 earnings ~Aug 4 — 12 weeks away. Position too small for partial trim to cover commission. Let it run.</p>\n        